value: Northeastern Siberia east from the Indigirka River, Wrangel Island, northern coast of Alaska, the Mackenzie delta, and Banks Island east to the Melville Peninsula, southern Baffin Island, and Hudson Bay (both coasts). Winters south to Japan, California, Arizona, Mexico (Chihuahua, Coahuila, Durango, Tamaulipas), Texas, Louisiana, central Atlantic coast of United States. Occasional Europe.

value: breeds from northeastern Siberia and Alaska to northwestern and north central Canada; winters in the southern United States from California to New York, and to northern Mexico
